### Configuracoes Iniciais (Variaveis)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

### 0. Login para obter token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "contato@opticaflow.com.br",
  "senha": "11222333000181"
}

###

@token = COLE_SEU_TOKEN
@empresaId = COLE_ID_EMPRESA
@filialId = COLE_ID_FILIAL
@fornecedorId = COLE_ID_FORNECEDOR
@compraId = COLE_ID_COMPRA

### ----------------------------------------------------------------------
### COMPRA
### ----------------------------------------------------------------------

### 1. Criar compra
POST {{baseUrl}}/compra
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "empresaId": "{{empresaId}}",
  "filialId": "{{filialId}}",
  "fornecedorId": "{{fornecedorId}}",
  "dataCompra": "2026-07-01T10:00:00.000Z",
  "status": "aberta",
  "observacoes": "Compra mensal de reposicao"
}

### 2. Listar compras por empresa
GET {{baseUrl}}/compra/empresa/{{empresaId}}?page=1&limit=10&search=reposicao&filialId={{filialId}}&fornecedorId={{fornecedorId}}&status=aberta
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Buscar compra por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/compra/{{compraId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Atualizar compra
PUT {{baseUrl}}/compra/{{compraId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "finalizada",
  "observacoes": "Compra conferida e finalizada"
}

### 5. Teste negativo: fornecedor de outra filial
POST {{baseUrl}}/compra
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "empresaId": "{{empresaId}}",
  "filialId": "{{filialId}}",
  "fornecedorId": "COLE_FORNECEDOR_DE_OUTRA_FILIAL"
}

### 6. Deletar compra (somente sem itens)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/compra/{{compraId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
